  "title": "descending at...",
  "sourceFile": "Burbank_notes/descend_N.htm",
  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>descending\n        at...</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>The line presumably refers to Freud's <em>Interpretation\n        of Dreams</em>. In the first draft the line read\n        \"And Triton blew his wrinkled shell.\" against\n        which Pound wrote \"if you 'hotel' this rhythm shd be\n        weighted a bit, I think.\" </font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\">Burbank</a>\n                and The Beautiful Dream</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Dreams_SF.htm\">Interpretation\n                of Dreams</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>the first draft</td>\n<td> </td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>discussion of Burbank and Bleistein</td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></font></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "descending at... The line presumably refers to Freud's Interpretation of Dreams . In the first draft the line read \"And Triton blew his wrinkled shell.\" against which Pound wrote \"if you 'hotel' this rhythm shd be weighted a bit, I think.\" reference topics Burbank and The Beautiful Dream Interpretation of Dreams the first draft discussion of Burbank and Bleistein back to \"Burbank\"",
